  "body": "BFT doesn't support the london hardfork with eip-1559 due to way the header validation rules are created. We will need to create the GasLimitRangeAndDeltaValidationRule header validation rule similarly to what was done for Clique.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**\n* IBFT2 network with London and Arrow Glacier hard forks can produce blocks\n* QBFT network with London and Arrow Glacier hard forks can produce blocks",
